This paper discusses the improvement of network capacity in cellular systems through network densification, higher frequency bands, and spectral efficiency enhancement techniques. These topics are closely related to the fields of networking (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), systems and control (cs.SY), and architecture (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
